{"tid":1802971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(劇透)從[返校]看時代革命","createTime":"2019-12-30T00:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T05:33:43.000Z","uid":183358,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3a246f8c77c36e35367e7578e5aa87e0f70e37","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:35:52.000Z","msg":"睇完返校感受好深， 究竟大家想成為(返校)入面嘅邊個角色？<br />\n<br />\n痛苦多年後先可以解放自己的魏仲廷嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還是</span><br />\n不斷輪迴否定事實不願意面對過去後悔一生最終自殺的方芮欣嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還是</span><br />\n被方芮欣告發無辜死去的讀書會七人嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還是</span><br />\n一群明知有不公嘅事發生，但因為恐懼強權而置諸不理嘅普通學生嗎？<br />\n<br />\n其實其實(返校)正正就係香港嘅縮影同未來， 唔想成為以上四種人希望大家可以行出嚟， 喺情況未變到最壞嘅時候，爭取我哋應有嘅權利同自由。<br />\n<br />\n2019-01-01維園見"},{"pid":"4b675eb2790f2222b214d37d6b3b5c3297318d96","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:36:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f313282bdd0094d721863d53f3045911675d0d92","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a660281978193b5b57ba918e1e3116919906930","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db81ded94d1ba389bc509cd92ffda9c6a16a5ca0","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fd1b0d3de4bd694ba6ab7d0ff189d0f6155e6c3","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:37:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d878a0dce91718a1e77b1d820aabb9e64434df7","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c5f319713ffd43f75188762a72caf790e61a916","tid":1802971,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T00:37:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p